---
title: Cheat's Moroccan Lamb Tagine with Mint Couscous & Yoghurt
description: Take a little bit of ras el hanout spice, some flavoursome lamb mince and a dash of mango chutney for sweetness, and what have you got? Why, it’s the perfect recipe for a delicious cheat's Moroccan lamb tagine!
